"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Even if it has brought a deep and comprehensive Internet to people's production and life, we can't confirm that it has brought changes in productivity and production relations. If we must find a footnote for the Internet, the greatest value and significance is only to change the way and method of people's communication and communication. In other words, the Internet still has not realized the transformation of the original productivity and production relations.\\n\\nIt is wrong to simply attribute this to the disadvantages of the Internet model. The short board of Internet technology is doomed by the fact that the means of production have not changed in the era of the Internet. When the pointer of time comes to the blockchain era, we see the birth and emergence of a new means of production dominated by numbers and data. In this context, blockchain has the conditions to reconstruct productivity and production relations.\\n\\nPeople who are used to the Internet style routine can not find the correct development mode and method of blockchain in any case, which is inevitable. It is also wrong to attribute this inevitability to blockchain technology, so it is also wrong to start trying to find a breakthrough in technology.\\n\\nWhat we really need is an ideological and cognitive revolution, which is the key to the real rebirth of the blockchain. Compared with the iteration and evolution of technology, the revolution in thought and cognition is more difficult, but it is imperative. Only in this way can a new generation truly belonging to the blockchain really come and the blockchain really shine from the ideal into the reality.\",\"timestamp\":1638977294,\"title\":\"Blockchain is a process of reconstructing productivity and production relations\"},\"digest\":\"X3LKddADpKtJgGwIELwbbvYED6FMmlJc0kpmeaChmFU\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x2dAEA6B39c2A34AbAaCE3F4c265f3C9377D37d81\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\